Cactus McCoy is an action-packed platformer where you control McCoy, a cactus hero on a quest to defeat enemies and uncover treasures. Explore dangerous dungeons, solve puzzles, and fight bosses in this exciting adventure!

⚔️ Objective: Navigate levels, defeat foes, and collect loot.
🎮 How to Play: Run, jump, and use weapons to overcome obstacles.
🔥 Tip: Upgrade your gear and master your moves to survive!

Get ready for a thrilling desert adventure with Cactus McCoy!

